## FILE: `.gitignore`

```gitignore
# Aegis OS — Git Ignore

# Local configuration
config/aegis.config.local.yaml
config/*.local.yaml

# Generated reports
reports/registry/*.tmp
reports/registry/*.log

# PowerShell temporary files
*.ps1xml
*.psc1
*.pssc
*.psd1.bak
*.ps1.bak

# Logs
*.log
logs/
tmp/
temp/

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# Editor files
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
!.vscode/settings.example.json
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# Node / frontend future tooling
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
dist/
build/
coverage/

# Python future tooling
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.pyo
*.pyd
.venv/
venv/
env/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/

# Package artifacts
*.tgz
*.zip
*.tar.gz

# Secrets and environment files
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Local CLI artifacts
.aegis/
aegis.local.json
```